<div class="jumbotron py-4 mb-3">
  <h1 class="display-4">Another Triple Triad Tracker</h1>
  <p class="lead">Another website for tracking your Final Fantasy XIV Triple Triad card collection.</p>
  <hr class="my-4">
  <h5>Easy setup</h5>
  <p>
    Create and maintain your card collection by matching up the website with your in-game card list.
  </p>
  <h5>Powered by the community</h5>
  <p>
    I'm relying on the community to keep my sources up to date. If you see a source that is missing or incorrect,
    please let me know on <%= link_to 'Discord', 'https://discord.gg/cTxYGYerpg', target: '_blank' %>.
  </p>
  <h5>Do you have feedback? I want to hear it!</h5>
  <p>
    The community is what motivates me to create these projects, so if you have any feedback,
    please let me know on <%= link_to 'Discord', 'https://discord.gg/bA9fYQjEYy', target: '_blank' %>.
  </p>
  <div class="mt-4 text-center">
    <%= link_to 'Discuss on Discord', 'https://discord.gg/QVypqNn2cg', class: 'btn discord mt-2', target: '_blank' %>
    <%= link_to 'Support on Patreon', 'https://www.patreon.com/raelys', class: 'btn patreon mt-2', target: '_blank' %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">
        <h5>API</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <p>
          All of the data used on this site is available for any savvy developers through a public RESTful JSON API.
          You can check out the full documentation
          <%= link_to 'here', api_docs_path, target: '_blank' %>.
        </p>
        <b>GET <%= link_to nil, api_card_url(240), class: 'unstyled' %></b>
        <%= render 'api_sample' %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-right mt-2">
      FINAL FANTASY is a registered trademark of Square Enix Holdings Co., Ltd.<br>
      FINAL FANTASY XIV Â© SQUARE ENIX CO., LTD.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
